headline: Nearly a Third of Americans Worry About Missing a Holiday Event Due to Illness
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., December 12, 2024--Staying healthy during the holiday season isn’t an easy task. According to a recent survey from Walgreens, 47 percent of Americans have missed a holiday event in recent years due to unexpected illness and nearly one in three are worried about it happening again this year.
